textBeforeTable: Written by Super User on 20 January 2015. Metro Sacco Business Centres   Originally, the SACCO was intended to serve primary school teachers in Kiambu District, Central Province. Over the years, the society’s common bond was opened to allow all interested Government employees within the Republic of Kenya to become members. Metropolitan National SACCO was registered on 10th February 1977 as Kiambu Teachers SACCO and continued to operate as such until 2nd July 2009 when we were granted the change of name certification.
